body:
Brie Larson quiere protagonizar una película de Metroid

Brie Larson está lista para asumir el papel principal de Samus Aran, en caso de que una película de Metroid obtenga luz verde.

La actriz de Captain Marvel se puso un disfraz de Samus Aran para Halloween. El traje de Larson provocó reacciones de los fanáticos de Metroid en todas partes, quienes comenzaron a especular sobre una nueva versión live action de la serie Nintendo.

title: Captain Marvel’s Brie Larson Wants To Make A Metroid Movie
body:
Captain Marvel’s Brie Larson Wants To Make A Metroid Movie

Captain Marvel star Brie Larson dressed up as Metroid character Samus Aran for Halloween, and now the actress says she wants to make a Metroid movie. She won an Oscar for her harrowing portrayal of a woman held hostage in Lenny Abrahamson’s Room, and now Larson is leveraging that success by entering the world of big-time franchise filmmaking with her role as the titular superhero in Captain…
